author: Isolde Walters For Mailonline
title: Kendall Jenner and Hailey Baldwin have lunch during NYFW | Daily Mail Online
text: Share this article Share Kendall seemed keen to take a break from the gowns and stilettos of high fashion as she donned a pair of moss green trainers and a casual Nike sweatshirt. She jazzed up her look with a silver handbag perfectly matching her jacket. PVC chic: Hailey still looked stylish on her day off in wet-look leggings teamed with a taupe jumper and matching floor-length cardigan Shady ladies: The models shielded their eyes with sunglasses despite the wintry weather Look at that: Kendall appeared to point something out to her pal as they left the cafe Hailey went for a different look altogether, pairing her risque leggings with a demure taupe polo neck and matching floor-length cardigan. The models have been hard at work at New York Fashion Week, one of the most important events in the fashion world's calendar. Kendall, a member of the Kardashian clan, closed luxury lingerie designer La Perla's first collection, wearing a see-through glittery lace dress. While her pal Hailey posted a picture on Instagram of herself looking weary at one of her many fittings. She captioned the image: 'I'm always tired in fittings.' All laced up: Kendall's trousers boasted intricate stitching emphasising her supermodel legs Take the lead: Kendall lagged behind her pal as they hurried into the cafe on a rare day off Catwalk queen: Kendall rocked a dramatic gothic ensemble on the Alexander Wang runway on Saturday All American girl: Hailey walked in the Tommy Hilfiger show in Los Angeles on Wednesday in an oversized sweat shirt, bare legs and buckled boots for her pal Gigi Hadid's collection with the brand Share or comment on this article Most watched News videos
